                           aligned letters.</p>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <!-- ********* <decoDesc> ********* -->
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote ana="#xx">
                        <ab>Sun-disc with small red painted triangles around it</ab>
                        <locus>Above the inscription. Its outline is heavily drawn in red
                           paint</locus>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote ana="#xx">
                        <ab>Cross formed of four triangulated bars, filled with grey paint, and of a
                           red painted circle in its centre </ab>
                        <locus>On the lower right corner of the inscription, roughly at the end of
                           the eleventh line. A similar cross could have existed in the lower left corner.</locus>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote>
                        <ab>Red painted cross-shaped frame with a zigzag pattern on its lower
                           vertical bar</ab>
                        <locus>Enclosing the inscription. It is now mostly faded.</locus>
